(1, 1, 'There is beautiful Netural.', '<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sequi eveniet temporibus quis neque repellendus, molestiae nostrum. Tenetur eos ut nostrum totam! Velit nemo aperiam laboriosam nisi commodi in aliquid fugiat et voluptates labore! Dolor, aliquid cupiditate quo blanditiis maiores aperiam deleniti odio modi eaque inventore eum repellat quos at. Nulla! Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sequi eveniet temporibus quis neque repellendus, molestiae nostrum. Tenetur eos ut nostrum totam! Velit nemo aperiam laboriosam nisi commodi in aliquid fugiat et voluptates labore! Dolor, aliquid cupiditate quo blanditiis maiores aperiam deleniti odio modi eaque inventore eum repellat quos at. Nulla!</p>', 'upload/726222cc4a.jpeg', 'admin', 'Netural, Technology', '2021-10-16 20:37:11'),
(2, 2, 'History of the Microsoft Windows Logo', '<p>Windows is among the products of the world\'s top companies. For years, Microsoft has grown the brand with a value of $326.5 billion. The operating system is what helped propel the corporation into astounding growth. It has bested its competitors and remained a household name since the \'80s.</p>\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s take a deep dive into the Windows logo\'s history and evolution. We will tackle both old and new Windows logos to give you an idea of how a tech company can brand itself for success. Jump into these bullets:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://blog.designcrowd.ca/article/1687/history-of-the-microsoft-windows-logo#Meet\">Meet the designer</a></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://blog.designcrowd.ca/article/1687/history-of-the-microsoft-windows-logo#Windows\">Windows logo meaning</a></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://blog.designcrowd.ca/article/1687/history-of-the-microsoft-windows-logo#Microsoft\">Microsoft Windows logo evolution</a></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong><a name=\"Meet\"></a>Meet the designer</strong></h2>\r\n<p>\"Your name is Windows. Why are you a flag?\"</p>\r\n<p>That\'s what Paula Scher from Pentagram asked the Microsoft team during the design process of the 2012 Windows logo. This memorable quote embodied the boldness of the logo\'s lead designer.</p>\r\n<p>Scher led the design in collaboration with Michael Beirut, Daniel Well, and Microsoft\'s in-house teams. Scher is a graphic designer under Pentagram, a design firm that has worked with a broad range of companies. The firm has worked with tech brands such as IBM, Yahoo, Oppo, and Slack.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\"The team spent a full day sharing some of the Metro style design philosophy; the Windows brand history and values as well as graphic design and technology industry trends,\" wrote Sam Moreau, Principal Director of User Experience for Windows in a blog post.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong><a name=\"Windows\"></a>Windows logo meaning</strong></h2>\r\n<p>The four-paneled brand mark of Windows has been around since the beginning. It\'s a straightforward way to represent the brand name. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandcrowd.com/maker/tag/tech\">tech logo</a>&nbsp;is similar to the way Apple\'s logo is a literal apple. However, this metaphor elegantly symbolizes the metaphor for computing.</p>\r\n<p>You may also notice that the current version of the logo is slanted. This is because the brand wanted to celebrate the concept of windows in perspective. Microsoft Windows wanted to symbolize how each user utilizes the software to match each need.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Their old&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.brandcrowd.com/maker/tag/flag\">flag logo</a>&nbsp;now was given a classical perspective, meaning the designers did not use computerized systems to create this design. This gives it depth and dimension, making the design more attention-grabbing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong><a name=\"Microsoft\"></a>Microsoft Windows logo evolution</strong></h2>\r\n<p>As a company matures, its tone, services, and consumer expectations shift as well. These changes are best reflected by a compelling visual identity.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Take a look at how the Windows logo variations have represented its growth over the years. This section will examine how Microsoft has kept its relevance by keeping up an updated visual identity.</p>', 'upload/7b77e45659.png', 'Admin', 'windows', '2021-10-16 20:39:06'),
(3, 2, '25 Drone Logo Designs to Take You Higher', '<p><span>When we say drones, we\'re not referring to our friendly honey making insect friends. Drones or maybe more accurately quadcopters are becoming more and more common. It\'s really not unusual to see a drone buzzing around residential areas taking in the sites and sounds. Not only are drones everywhere, drone businesses have really \"taken off\" (pun intended!) with the world largest drone seller making an unimaginable&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://technode.com/2018/01/03/worlds-top-drone-seller-dji-made-2-7-billion-2017/\">$2.7 billion in 2017</a><span>.</span><br /><br /><span>With drone centric businesses offering everything from aerial photography and videography (dronography anyone?) to 3d terrain mapping and even private investigation - it\'s no wonder the demand for&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://logo.designcrowd.ca/logo-design-gallery/technology/drone-logos\">drone logos</a><span>&nbsp;has also skyrocketed. Drone businesses looking to crack the quadcopter market adopt design inspiration from the drones themselves, but often take inspiration from&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://logo.designcrowd.ca/logo-design-gallery/company/professional-service/photographer-logos\">photography logos</a><span>,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://logo.designcrowd.ca/logo-design-gallery/technology\">technology company logos</a><span>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://logo.designcrowd.ca/logo-design-gallery/company/startup-logos\">tech start up sector</a><span>.</span></p>', 'upload/5efd75d511.png', 'Admin', 'Design', '2021-10-16 20:38:52'),
(7, 2, '5 Forex Careers for Financial Professionals', '<p><em>Many people in Bangladesh are involved in forex trading. However, it is not yet legalized in Bangladesh. Therefore, traders from Bangladesh are unable to trade in the forex market like local DSE or CSE. However, still, there are some ways to trade forex from Bangladesh using several online payment gateways and Brokers.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><strong>30 November 2020,<a href=\"https://atozmarkets.com/\">&nbsp;AtoZ Markets</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;</strong>As you know, Forex is the largest financial market in the world, with more than 5 trillion dollar transactions on a daily basis. Making profit from Forex trading is one of the effective ways to make money with your investments. Due to globalization and the increase of technology, people can buy or sell their favorite currency pairs from home. This makes Forex trading easy for Bangladeshi traders. However, it is essential to know how to trade in the forex market before making any investment.</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To start forex trading in Bangladesh, you also need to know some points about Forex Trading.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span>What is Forex?</span></h2>\r\n<p>The forex market is a unique place to buy and sell currencies worldwide. It is a decentralized global market where all the world&rsquo;s currencies trade through different exchanges.&nbsp;<span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">This means buying and selling foreign currencies like USD, EUR, CAD, CHF, GBP, and some commodities like gold, silver, and oil against other currencies. The unique feature of the forex market is that it is decentralized and it is the world&rsquo;s most liquid market.&nbsp;</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">No one has control over the market and no one can dominate it. The forex market is open 24 hours and 5 days a week and traders can trade any time that is suitable for him. However,&nbsp;</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">here are four main sessions in a day for the forex traders. They are the New York market, the London market, the Tokyo market, and the Sydney market.</span></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-80423 aligncenter jetpack-lazy-image jetpack-lazy-image--handled\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/atozmarkets.com/wp-content/uploads/amicus/2019/11/rsz_courses-643727_960_720.jpg?resize=410%2C308&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"410\" height=\"308\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" data-lazy-loaded=\"1\" /></p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The main participants of the forex market are a large number of government &amp; non-governmental financial institutions, banks, hedge funds &amp; mutual funds.&nbsp; However, the involvement of retail traders in the forex market is not much comparing to investment giants. Therefore, retail trading is quite hard comparing to institutional trading. But now they have allowed small forex trading investors under an authorized Forex broker.</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As technology has been improved, the involvement of the retail traders has been increased dramatically.&nbsp; Now, it doesn&rsquo;t matter where the trader lives. A young boy from Bangladesh with a piece of good knowledge about technical and fundamental analysis can beat the big investors.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span>Forex Trading from Bangladesh</span></h2>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In some countries, forex trading is illegal or has some restrictions for forex trading. These countries are&nbsp;<strong>Belarus, China, India, Iran, Saudi Arabia, Canada, Pakistan, South Korea, Japan, and Turkey</strong>. Bangladesh is not one of these countries but foreign exchange regulation in Bangladesh is not friendly for traders.</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The Bangladesh Bank (BB) regulates the Forex transactions in Bangladesh. Only Bangladeshi banks and their authorized money exchangers can make FX transactions. The legislation states that licensed brokers can sell FX products under the Foreign Exchange Regulation Act 1947. The general people, along with the Bangladeshis living abroad are not authorized to perform foreign exchange transactions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As it is a highly potential platform, everyone wants to know how to trade Forex from Bangladesh. Many traders are doing this business from Bangladesh and earning a lot of foreign remittances. However, it is a risky job for newbies.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://atozmarkets.com/news/forex-trading-is-a-skill-not-a-shortcut-to-riches/\"><strong>Forex trading is a skill, not a shortcut to riches</strong></a>. There are certain ways to start forex trading from Bangladesh. In this article, we will see some steps of forex trading in Bangladesh:-&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><strong>Finding a Right Broker</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To start forex trading from Bangladesh, traders should find a broker that allows registration from Bangladesh. Retail currency trading has evolved as a decentralized and regulated activity in an over-the-counter market. Therefore, traders should research the reputation of brokers before opening a trading account.</span></p>', 'upload/5220ef4928.jpeg', 'Admin', 'Forex', '2021-10-16 20:47:47');

